---
// components/about/AboutHero.astro
---

<section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero__container">
      <div class="about-hero__grid">
        
        <div class="about-hero__image">
          <img src="/chairs/exclusive-chair.jpg" alt="Chaise KWESK" />
        </div>
  
        <div class="about-hero__content">
          <span class="about-hero__label">Notre Entreprise</span>
          
          <h1 class="about-hero__title">
            KWESK<br/>
            LEADER DES<br/>
            CHAISES<br/>
            CORPORATE
          </h1>
          
          <p class="about-hero__desc">
            KWESK conçoit et fabrique des chaises pour une utilisation intensive au bureau ou à la maison.
          </p>
  
          <div class="about-hero__quote">
            <span class="about-hero__quote-mark">"</span>
            <p class="about-hero__quote-text">
              Au-delà de la robustesse unanime de tous les produits KWESK, nos ingénieurs concentrent leurs efforts sur l'innovation toujours dans le but d'offrir des mobiliers qui dépassent les attentes des entreprises.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="about-hero__author">
            <p class="about-hero__author-name">Tarik Benjelloun</p>
            <p class="about-hero__author-role">Fondateur, PDG de KWESK</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <style>
    .about-hero {
      padding: 120px 0;
    }
  
    .about-hero__container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 60px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 100px;
      align-items: center;
    }
  
    .about-hero__image img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  
    .about-hero__label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: #8b8b4b;
    }
  
    .about-hero__title {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1c1917;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__desc {
      color: #78716c;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__quote {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 70px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__quote-mark {
      font-size: 50px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #8b8b4b;
    }
  
    .about-hero__quote-text {
      color: #57534e;
      text-align: justify;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }
  
    .about-hero__author {
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__author-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1c1917;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  
    .about-hero__author-role {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #a8a29e;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
  
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-hero__grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 60px;
      }
  
      .about-hero__title {
        font-size: 36px;
      }
  
      .about-hero__container {
        padding: 0 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>